{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":312,"text":"I collaborate with bacteria."},{"time":2450,"text":"And I'm about to show you"},{"time":3332,"text":"some stop-motion footage that I made recently"},{"time":5512,"text":"where you'll see bacteria accumulating minerals"},{"time":7746,"text":"from their environment"},{"time":9296,"text":"over the period of an hour."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11230,"text":"So what you're seeing here"},{"time":12595,"text":"is the bacteria metabolizing,"},{"time":14813,"text":"and as they do so"},{"time":16012,"text":"they create an electrical charge."},{"time":17618,"text":"And this attracts metals"},{"time":19951,"text":"from their local environment."},{"time":22118,"text":"And these metals accumulate as minerals"},{"time":25035,"text":"on the surface of the bacteria."}]},{"cues":[{"time":26952,"text":"One of the most pervasive problems"},{"time":29119,"text":"in the world today for people"},{"time":30868,"text":"is inadequate access"},{"time":32285,"text":"to clean drinking water."},{"time":34036,"text":"And the desalination process"},{"time":35702,"text":"is one where we take out salts."},{"time":37486,"text":"We can use it for drinking and agriculture."},{"time":40001,"text":"Removing the salts from water --"},{"time":42086,"text":"particularly seawater --"},{"time":43347,"text":"through reverse osmosis"},{"time":44951,"text":"is a critical technique"},{"time":46269,"text":"for countries who do not have access to clean drinking water"},{"time":49501,"text":"around the globe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50620,"text":"So seawater reverse osmosis"},{"time":52084,"text":"is a membrane-filtration technology."},{"time":54251,"text":"We take the water from the sea"},{"time":56821,"text":"and we apply pressure."},{"time":58352,"text":"And this pressure forces the seawater"},{"time":61276,"text":"through a membrane."},{"time":62576,"text":"This takes energy,"},{"time":64011,"text":"producing clean water."},{"time":66543,"text":"But we're also left with a concentrated salt solution, or brine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":70244,"text":"But the process is very expensive"},{"time":71657,"text":"and it's cost-prohibitive for many countries around the globe."},{"time":74291,"text":"And also, the brine that's produced"},{"time":76073,"text":"is oftentimes just pumped back out into the sea."},{"time":78957,"text":"And this is detrimental to the local ecology"},{"time":81505,"text":"of the sea area that it's pumped back out into."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83940,"text":"So I work in Singapore at the moment,"},{"time":85956,"text":"and this is a place that's really a leading place"},{"time":88723,"text":"for desalination technology."},{"time":90724,"text":"And Singapore proposes by 2060"},{"time":93274,"text":"to produce [900] million liters per day"},{"time":96373,"text":"of desalinated water."},{"time":98206,"text":"But this will produce an equally massive amount"},{"time":101556,"text":"of desalination brine."},{"time":103309,"text":"And this is where my collaboration with bacteria comes into play."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106507,"text":"So what we're doing at the moment"},{"time":108456,"text":"is we're accumulating metals"},{"time":111122,"text":"like calcium, potassium and magnesium"},{"time":113106,"text":"from out of desalination brine."},{"time":115340,"text":"And this, in terms of magnesium"},{"time":117622,"text":"and the amount of water that I just mentioned,"},{"time":120172,"text":"equates to a $4.5 billion"},{"time":123122,"text":"mining industry for Singapore --"},{"time":125537,"text":"a place that doesn't have any natural resources."}]},{"cues":[{"time":128071,"text":"So I'd like you to image a mining industry"},{"time":130721,"text":"in a way that one hasn't existed before;"},{"time":132810,"text":"imagine a mining industry"},{"time":134976,"text":"that doesn't mean defiling the Earth;"},{"time":137243,"text":"imagine bacteria helping us do this"},{"time":139354,"text":"by accumulating and precipitating"},{"time":142826,"text":"and sedimenting minerals"},{"time":145243,"text":"out of desalination brine."},{"time":147092,"text":"And what you can see here"},{"time":148510,"text":"is the beginning of an industry in a test tube,"},{"time":150992,"text":"a mining industry that is in harmony with nature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":154342,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155693,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}